    <td class="table" colspan="2">
      <pre style="font: 9pt Courier New, Tahoma, MS Sans Serif, Microsoft Sans Serif, Verdana, AngsanaUPC, CordiaUPC; padding: 10px;">
        SET adds new listed securities: AKR

   The Stock Exchange of Thailand (SET) reported 
that the SET's board has granted a listing of common 
shares of Ekarat Engineering Public Company Limited
from 7 August 2006 onwards.

   The SET has set common shares of Ekarat Engineering 
Public Company Limited, amounting to 790,173,640 shares 
with a par value of Baht 1 per share totaling of Baht 
790,173,640 to be traded on the SET under Industry group of 
Resources, Energy and Utilities sector and using the trading 
name of "AKR" commencing from 7 August 2006.

Note: Please see the Information Memorandum of AKR
disseminated on the SET Market Analysis and Reporting
Tool (SETSMART) and AKR's information from 
website: http:// www.ekarat-transformer.com


                                     Information Memorandum  

                   Ekarat Engineering Public Company Limited ("AKR")

Head Office         9/291U.M. Tower 28th Floor, Ramkhamhaeng Road, 
                    Suanluang District, Bangkok 10250 
                    Tel. 02-719 8777 (automatic 30 lines) 
                    Fax. 02-719-8760-2 

Website             www.ekarat-transformer.com 

Factory             190/1 Moo 6, Thasa-An, Bangpakong, Chachoengsao.
                    260 Thasa-An, Bangpakong, Chachoengsao.
Branch Office       AKR has 10 sales and service centers nationwide.
  
Listing Date        August 7, 2006 (First day trade August 7, 2006) 

Listing Securities      
     Common stock 790,173,640 shares, par value Baht 1 per share. Total value
of Baht 790,173,640. 
     (The Company issued and IPO for 182,000,000 newly issued common share)

Secondary Market    The Stock Exchange of Thailand (SET)

Offering Price      Baht 2.70 per share

Offering Period     25-27 July 2006 

Objectives and plans for utilizing the capital increase
     1. Use as Working Capital for Ekarat Engineering Public Co.,Ltd. 
("AKR" or "the company") in the amount of Baht 3.09 million.
     2. Use as investment for Ekarat Solar Co.,Ltd. to construct factory 
and purchase machines to produce solar cell in the amount of Baht 470 million.

Green Shoe Option (if any)      - None -

Type of business and Nature of operation        
     AKR manufactures and distributes 3 types of services: transformers, 
service and energy.
     1) Distribution transformer is manufactured and distributed by AKR from
1kVA to 20,000kVA oil & dry transformer and  also manufactures transformer 
accessories.
     2) The service that AKR is providing to customers includes maintenance, 
modification & repair of transformers. The company has 10 sales and service 
centers nationwide.
     3) Power energy, provided by AKR is in a form of design and installation
from the solar system as well as energy conservation.

