     The connected transactions are comply with the AKR's policy to discontinue
all transactions with 8 companies which AKR has divested its shareholding. 
After divestment, these are 5 companies have seized their operation and can
not make any profitability again. These are 3 companies still operate. The 
transfer claimant rights on debt to E.K.R. Holding Co.,Ltd. to chase up 
liabilities will be good for the company because the cost of chasing up 
liabilities will be higher than liabilities should be concentrate on its core 
business. 

